Package rajawali.scenegraph

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IGraphNode
    Generic interface allowing for the incorporation of scene graphs to the rendering pipeline of Rajawali.
    IGraphNodeMember
    Generic interface which any member of IGraphNode must implement in order to be a part of the graph.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    A_nAABBTree
    Generic Axis Aligned Bounding Box based tree sorting hierarchy.
    Octree
    Octree implementation specific to the Rajawali library.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IGraphNode.GRAPH_TYPE
    This enum defines the different scene graphs which RajawaliScene can use.
